                <h1>Mercedes-Benz: A Legacy of Innovation and Luxury</h1>
                <p>Mercedes-Benz's history began in 1886 with Karl Benz's invention of the first gasoline-powered automobile. The brand evolved through the merger of Benz & Cie and Daimler-Motoren-Gesellschaft in 1926. Known for innovation, luxury, and performance, Mercedes-Benz has set automotive benchmarks, continually advancing technology and design.</p>
